com.corvolution.mesana.data

Class Measurement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.corvolution.mesana.rest.RestApiConnector
      • com.corvolution.mesana.data.Measurement

  • public class Measurement
extends RestApiConnector
    This class represents Measurement service object.This object must not be mistaken with a sensor data after measuring completed. When customer orders service it is meant to send configurated sensor for measuring.Before configuration one must have specific information and this class is used for that purpose.
    Author:
    Suleyman Gasimov
